To obtain examples of condition files, data files, and the geographic data required to prepare these datasets, please visit [https://cloud.tsinghua.edu.cn/d/d51d3d9a936e463eba9e/] to preview and download them.

Please ensure that the file structure in this directory is organized as follows:

datasets
├── cities
│   ├── Nanjing
│   │   ├── cond
│   │   │   └── Nanjing_cond.npz
│   │   ├── data
│   │   │   ├── Nanjing_traffic_data.npz
│   │   │   └── Nanjing_user_data.npz
│   │   ├── raw_data_for_train
│   │   │   ├── Nanjing_traffic.npz
│   │   │   └── Nanjing_user.npz
│   │   └── geographic_data
│   │       ├── OSM_Jiangsu
│   │       └── POI_Nanjing
│
│   └── Nanchang
│       ├── cond
│       │   └── Nanchang_cond.npz
│       ├── data
│       │   ├── Nanchang_traffic_data.npz
│       │   └── Nanchang_user_data.npz
│       ├── raw_data_for_train
│       │   ├── Nanchang_traffic.npz
│       │   └── Nanchang_user.npz
│       └── geographic_data
│           ├── OSM_Jiangxi
│           └── POI_Nanchang
│
├── _data_preparation
│   ├── Grid_meta.py
│   ├── Env_extra.py
│   ├── funcs.py
│   ├── organize_geographic_data.py
│   └── src
│       ├── Env_gen.sh
│       └── Grid_meta_gen.sh
│
├── _shared_geographic_data
│   ├── chn_ppp_2020_constrained.tif
│   ├── China_city_boundaries
│   └── Readme
│
├── template_scaler_traffic.pkl
├── template_scaler_user.pkl
├── template_traffic.npz
└── template_user.npz

Each city should be placed under `cities` with its English directory name. The runtime loaders also accept supported Chinese city names and map them to the corresponding English dataset directory.
